{"tid":1923144,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"秋生阿澤斥警方作威作福","createTime":"2020-03-13T02:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T02:26:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"15bdc9df1630301c2cf3b5dea754f13745d42205","tid":1923144,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:22:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200311/SOUGYUHOVYSCPWHXM2RJEHL66U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200311%2FSOUGYUHOVYSCPWHXM2RJEHL66U%2F&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=7d254e91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200311%2FSOUGYUHOVYSCPWHXM2RJEHL66U%2F&h=f8d23b65\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200311/SOUGYUHOVYSCPWHXM2RJEHL66U/</a><br />\n<br />\n秋生阿澤斥警方作威作福<br />\n<br />\n黃秋生及杜汶澤前晚先後在社交網聲討警方，因周日警方在將軍澳粗暴對待悼念周梓樂的市民，更有網媒拍到七名蒙面警察辱罵一位路過市民，並要求該市民逐一向在場七警道歉。秋生貼出該片並留言：「唔知邊個硬冷膠呢？仲好意思講法治，法治畀你班契弟作威作福嘅？」絕大部份網民留言都一面倒指摘警方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583845564_7e78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583845564_7e78.jpg&h=24c59267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秋生直斥警察是契弟在作威作福。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤也留言狂轟：「人渣鄧炳強（PK鄧）口中的假新聞&hellip;&hellip;牛丸、魚蛋、魚片、貢丸、墨魚丸、魚皮餃、雲吞、水餃圍X人。」有網民從心理角度分析，認為警方借機取暖：「心理反射箒，得唔到香港人認同，所以咪逼手無寸鐵嘅人講一啲佢哋想聽嘅嘢囉。」更有網民指稱警察根本缺乏家庭教養：「港警的家教很差，他們爸媽沒教好的錯。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：余嬌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583845563_d736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583845563_d736.jpg&h=4d6d3a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿澤寸圍市民的七警是牛丸、魚蛋。資料圖片"},{"pid":"6641c2c23fa9c0a7dbcb9d0d4faf0b0b4bdad2d9","tid":1923144,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"又有中學生派口罩 但唔夠人推搞到無人知 想幫學生都幫唔到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1923133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1923133</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}